Ref 2:
Init counter to one
init number to zero
init largest number to zero

while counter less than or equal to 10
    prompt for a number
    input the number
    set it as the largest if its bigger than the largest

display the largest

Ref 3:
init counter to one
init number to zero
init largest to zero

while counter is less than or equal to ten
    prompt the user for a number
    input the number

    if the number is greater than the largest
        set largest to number

    increment counter
display a newline and the largest number
